{"tid":59373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬚後水製佳釀巴基斯坦聖誕毒酒派對42死150人留醫","createTime":"2016-12-29T14:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T17:21:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1a5f13c89acd4ebfa6a5eca074e3d18991d5f2","tid":59373,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/328804/xlarge/a3f6942a5689c244f362771fdcc3c705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F328804%2Fxlarge%2Fa3f6942a5689c244f362771fdcc3c705.jpg&h=d6668963&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大批民眾飲用毒酒後死亡。(互聯網) <br />\n<br />\n繼俄羅斯本月有逾60人飲用含酒精淋浴消毒水死亡後，巴基斯坦再發生類似事件。該國東旁遮普(Punjab)多巴代格辛格(Toba Tek Singh)聖誕節一個由基督徒舉辦的派對中，多人飲用自行釀製的酒精飲料後出現嚴重不適徵狀，至今已造成42死亡，150人留醫。 <br />\n<br />\n當地警方調查事件後，相信4人為派對準備酒精飲料時，加入有毒物質，他們1人死亡，2人情況危殆，餘下1人正被警方拘留，他承認釀酒時加入20公升鬚後水和不同化學物質，相信酒內含有甲醇。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，多名受害者周日飲酒後跳舞狂舞狂歡，至翌日早上感到不適，到醫院求醫，部份人接着陷入昏迷，繼而死亡。死者遍及鎮內各個家庭，當中包括5名穆斯林，鎮上一片愁雲慘霧，家人忙於為死者準備身後事。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/328805/xlarge/55fcb6e9e1863a1a02ffb7a6676f5675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F328805%2Fxlarge%2F55fcb6e9e1863a1a02ffb7a6676f5675.jpg&h=ea9fcaa0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦是傳統伊斯蘭教國家，不論穆斯林、少數族裔和外國人都禁止飲酒，亦禁止銷售酒精飲品。由於黑市酒類價格昂貴，不少民眾會自行釀酒飲用，曾多次造成中毒事件。 <br />\n<br />\n《半島電視台》"},{"pid":"a771942bad31903e1f02669b2f126affb7d96d7d","tid":59373,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"條女幾ok"},{"pid":"2ee5b7bc06176e97951e02f567bad988061ef3f5","tid":59373,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"穆斯林唔係好守教規架咩?<br />\n自己宗教禁止飲酒又走去自己整酒飲?"},{"pid":"8f78b852f63df050966a6c7cc1a9123318742168","tid":59373,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T19:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女幾ok</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好靚"},{"pid":"c07ffcac6247a737012d2bb94e0ee25353e7671a","tid":59373,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穆斯林唔係好守教規架咩?<br />\n自己宗教禁止飲酒又走去自己整酒飲?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n該國東旁遮普(Punjab)多巴代格辛格(Toba Tek Singh)聖誕節一個由基督徒舉辦的派對中"},{"pid":"63e62c84eda7343b2eefe4174e5604bbf31ca29e","tid":59373,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:42:22.000Z","msg":"Stupidity."},{"pid":"474cf2e6eff1dd0bd71e8bb94af86689482813be","tid":59373,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb19e7f88f68350af8bad7fafc3dcb81b7da4ba9","tid":59373,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6392ffdf7e44ebb866cb536ba5c15c1fd92c75a","tid":59373,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}